      "value": "<p>Your knowledge of your own biology gives you the ability to attempt a dramatic trick to survive a knockout blow.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Int 17</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> You attempt to survive a knockout blow by taking the strike to a less critical part of your anatomy. Once per day, when damage from a weapon attack would reduce you to 0 Hit Points, you can attempt a @Check[type:fortitude]{Fortitude save} with a DC equal to 10 + 1-1/2 times the attackerâ€™s CR. If you succeed at the Fortitude save, the attack instead reduces you to 1 HP. If you fail the save, you lose a Resolve Point.</p>"
